name				dcl
version				0.1
categories			sysutils
platforms			darwin linux
license				GPL-2+
revision			1
maintainers			gmail.com:fernando.iazeolla
description			D-cleaner -- Disk && Directory Cleaner 
long_description	\
		given a path **dcl** will clean this directory, and eventually subdirs, from a customazible \
		list of files, and eventually unmount or eject the volume.
					
